  "description": "A true symbol of passion and elegance, this lab-grown ruby ring is set in high-quality S925 sterling silver, offering durability and comfort with a hypoallergenic finish. The timeless design of this piece makes it perfect for any occasion, combining modern craftsmanship with classic beauty.\n\nAt the center of this stunning ring is a 6.6x8.5mm, 2.12-carat pear-cut lab-grown ruby, celebrated for its rich, fiery red color that symbolizes love and vitality. The center stone is beautifully complemented by two pear-shaped accent stones, one on each side, totaling 0.58 carats. The smooth, polished band weighs 2.6 grams, making it light yet substantial—perfect for daily wear or as a statement piece for special occasions. available in sizes 5 to 7.5 (standard U.S. sizing). Please note that lab-grown colored gemstone rings have an estimated shipping time of 3-15 days.\n\nKey Features:\n\nLab-Grown Ruby Center Stone: 6.6x8.5mm, 2.12-carat pear-cut ruby with a deep red hue.\n\nPear-Shaped Accent Stones: Two pear-cut stones, one on each side, totaling 0.58 carats, adding extra brilliance and sophistication.\n\nS925 Sterling Silver: Hypoallergenic, tarnish-resistant, and crafted to last for everyday elegance.\n\nComfortable Fit: Weighs 2.6 grams, offering a perfect balance of luxury and wearability.\n\nWith its vibrant ruby center and delicate pear-shaped accents, this ring is the ideal choice for those who appreciate timeless beauty with a touch of modern elegance.",
